title: Peach Cobbler
directions: In an 8 x 8 baking dish, stir Bisquick mix, milk, nutmeg and cinnamon together until thoroughly mixed. Stir in melted butter until crust is fully moistened. In a medium mixing bowl, stir sugar and peaches. Spoon peaches over the cobbler crust.
ingredients: 2 cups fresh sliced peaches (or one 29 ounce can of sliced peaches, drained)
